<%= render "shared/header" %>

<div class="main">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="side-image">
      <%= image_tag "top-sweets.png", class: "top-img" %>
      <%= image_tag "top-coffee.png", class: "bottom-img" %>
    </div>
    <div class="slide" id="makeImg">
      <%= image_tag "sepia.640.png", class:"img" %>
      <%= image_tag "tea.sepia.png", class:"img" %>
      <%= image_tag "sweets.sepia.png", class:"img" %>
      <%= image_tag "cafe.sepia.png", class:"img" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="contents">
    <h1>あなたはまだ出会っていないかもしれない...<br>運命とも思える<span>最高の一杯に</span></h1>
    <h2>目的</h2>
    <ul div class="purpose">
        <li><%= link_to 'コーヒー', "#", class: "genre" %></li>
        <li><%= link_to '紅茶', "#", class: "genre" %></li>
        <li><%= link_to 'スイーツ', "#", class: "genre" %></li>
        <li><%= link_to 'オシャレ', "#", class: "genre" %></li>
    </ul>
    <h2>地域</h2>
      <ul div class="place">
        <li><%= link_to "東京",search_cafes_path(region: 1), class:"btn-region", method: :get %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "北海道",search_cafes_path(region: 2), class:"btn-region", method: :get %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "東北",search_cafes_path(region: 3), class:"btn-region", method: :get %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "関東",search_cafes_path(region: 4), class:"btn-region", method: :get %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "中部",search_cafes_path(region: 5), class:"btn-region", method: :get %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "関西",search_cafes_path(region: 6), class:"btn-region", method: :get %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "中国",search_cafes_path(region: 7), class:"btn-region", method: :get %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "四国",search_cafes_path(region: 8), class:"btn-region", method: :get %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "九州",search_cafes_path(region: 9), class:"btn-region", method: :get %></li>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  <%= image_tag "plant-698637_640.jpg", class:"footer-img" %>
  <div class="message">
    <h2>カフェに求めるものはなんですか？<br><span>あなたにも運命の出会いがありますように...</span></h2>
    <%= image_tag "coffee.girl.png", class:"footer-girl" %>
  </div>
</div>